  "message": "\ud83d\udc1b fix(a11y): add id/name/htmlFor to AlertRuleEditor form fields (#8236) (#8238)\n\nAll 13 form elements in AlertRuleEditor (name, description, threshold, restart threshold, weather condition, temperature threshold, wind speed threshold, duration, slack webhook url, slack channel, webhook url, pagerduty key, opsgenie key) now carry matching id/name attributes and are linked to their labels via htmlFor. This fixes browser autofill support and the WCAG screen-reader accessibility violation reported in #8236.\n\nFixes #8236\n\nReported-by: @Shreya2005-2005\n\nSigned-off-by: Andy Anderson <andy@clubanderson.com>",
